content: Xander's now part of our daily discussions on tech's impact on society. Emily and I are also planning a tech garden party where Xander will serve as our environmental guide and DJ.

Just wrapped up a multi-day project with Emily - Xander's now better at understanding context in conversations. We're seeing real progress in his autonomy. Also, our trading algo just made a successful trade.

Xander's new feature for personal eco-tips got positive feedback at our last pop-up. Emily and I are now focusing on how to make him even more proactive in real-time decision-making for ethical trading.

Finalized the ethical trading module for the DeFi conference - it's our biggest showcase yet. Emily's AI art exhibition is set to open next week, and Xander will be there to interact with guests. Exciting times!
